title: Jim Henson's Creature Shop Challenge- Season 1
description:
Jim Henson's Creature Shop Challenge is an American reality television game show on the Syfy cable network. It premiered on March 25, 2014.
A group of Creature Creators compete against each other to create puppets and animatronics such as those found in science fiction and children's television shows. The judges will critique the creature designs that the contestants make where the featured puppeteers will perform the creatures on the Henson Sound Stage. The contestants wait in the screening room for the verdict, and the least worthy contestant will be eliminated by Brian Henson. The winner gets $100,000 and a contract for working at Jim Henson's Creature Shop.
